QuestData.Title: Eel Jelly
QuestData.Description:
<You examine the corpse of the abyssal eel, only to find it bathed in a strange slime.
The slime coats your hands and arms, and seems quite difficult to remove.
One of your deep sea allies may know more about it.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Eel Jelly to Artisan Itanu in Mezzamere in Nazjatar.
